The '''magic comp bow''' requires level 50 [[Ranged]] to wield, and can fire [[arrows]] up to [[amethyst arrows|amethyst]]. It is slightly quicker and more accurate than a [[magic longbow]], and features the same [[special attack]]. Magic comp bows can be obtained as a reward for completing a hard [[Treasure Trail]]. {{Costume storage|treasure chest}}

Composite bows can be fired from 10 [[attack range|squares away]] at both rapid and long range styles; this combination of speed and distance is matched only by the [[crystal bow]], [[scorching bow]], and [[bow of Faerdhinen]]. Where long attack distance is ideal, a magic comp bow could suffice as a non-degradable alternative to the crystal bow.

